cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect satire in Bangla documents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves feature extraction and classification, which are common topics in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of CNN architecture for classification suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
